Figaro</a>，<a href="http://www.wmagazine.com/fashion/2014/10/jonathan-anderson-loewe/photos/slide/6" style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">Wmagazine</a>，<a href="http://i-dandified.blogspot.com/" style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">I-dandified</a>&nbsp;，<a href="http://nowfashion.com/loewe-ready-to-wear-fall-winter-2015-paris-13880" style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">Now
Fashion</a>
</p>
		</div>
